{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":703,"text":"Let's face it:"},{"time":2617,"text":"Driving is dangerous."},{"time":5062,"text":"It's one of the things that we don't like to think about,"},{"time":8160,"text":"but the fact that religious icons and good luck charms"},{"time":11812,"text":"show up on dashboards around the world"},{"time":16602,"text":"betrays the fact that we know this to be true."},{"time":20739,"text":"Car accidents are the leading cause of death"},{"time":24333,"text":"in people ages 16 to 19 in the United States --"},{"time":28503,"text":"leading cause of death --"},{"time":31346,"text":"and 75 percent of these accidents have nothing to do"},{"time":35209,"text":"with drugs or alcohol."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37494,"text":"So what happens?"},{"time":39755,"text":"No one can say for sure, but I remember my first accident."},{"time":43974,"text":"I was a young driver out on the highway,"},{"time":47777,"text":"and the car in front of me, I saw the brake lights go on."},{"time":50035,"text":"I'm like, \"Okay, all right, this guy is slowing down,"},{"time":51835,"text":"I'll slow down too.\""},{"time":53117,"text":"I step on the brake."},{"time":55043,"text":"But no, this guy isn't slowing down."},{"time":57297,"text":"This guy is stopping, dead stop, dead stop on the highway."},{"time":60475,"text":"It was just going 65 -- to zero?"},{"time":63015,"text":"I slammed on the brakes."},{"time":64535,"text":"I felt the ABS kick in, and the car is still going,"},{"time":67594,"text":"and it's not going to stop, and I know it's not going to stop,"},{"time":70290,"text":"and the air bag deploys, the car is totaled,"},{"time":73229,"text":"and fortunately, no one was hurt."},{"time":76786,"text":"But I had no idea that car was stopping,"},{"time":80997,"text":"and I think we can do a lot better than that."},{"time":84642,"text":"I think we can transform the driving experience"},{"time":88787,"text":"by letting our cars talk to each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92666,"text":"I just want you to think a little bit"},{"time":94090,"text":"about what the experience of driving is like now."},{"time":96978,"text":"Get into your car. Close the door. You're in a glass bubble."},{"time":101006,"text":"You can't really directly sense the world around you."},{"time":103922,"text":"You're in this extended body."},{"time":106103,"text":"You're tasked with navigating it down"},{"time":108266,"text":"partially-seen roadways,"},{"time":110322,"text":"in and amongst other metal giants, at super-human speeds."},{"time":114746,"text":"Okay? And all you have to guide you are your two eyes."},{"time":119226,"text":"Okay, so that's all you have,"},{"time":120988,"text":"eyes that weren't really designed for this task,"},{"time":122723,"text":"but then people ask you to do things like,"},{"time":126474,"text":"you want to make a lane change,"},{"time":128023,"text":"what's the first thing they ask you do?"},{"time":130344,"text":"Take your eyes off the road. That's right."},{"time":133439,"text":"Stop looking where you're going, turn,"},{"time":135535,"text":"check your blind spot,"},{"time":137553,"text":"and drive down the road without looking where you're going."},{"time":141024,"text":"You and everyone else. This is the safe way to drive."},{"time":144159,"text":"Why do we do this? Because we have to,"},{"time":146400,"text":"we have to make a choice, do I look here or do I look here?"},{"time":148979,"text":"What's more important?"},{"time":150500,"text":"And usually we do a fantastic job"},{"time":153211,"text":"picking and choosing what we attend to on the road."},{"time":156980,"text":"But occasionally we miss something."},{"time":160630,"text":"Occasionally we sense something wrong or too late."},{"time":165091,"text":"In countless accidents, the driver says,"},{"time":167079,"text":"\"I didn't see it coming.\""},{"time":169387,"text":"And I believe that. I believe that."},{"time":172668,"text":"We can only watch so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175593,"text":"But the technology exists now that can help us improve that."},{"time":180737,"text":"In the future, with cars exchanging data with each other,"},{"time":185033,"text":"we will be able to see not just three cars ahead"},{"time":188961,"text":"and three cars behind, to the right and left,"},{"time":190555,"text":"all at the same time, bird's eye view,"},{"time":193721,"text":"we will actually be able to see into those cars."},{"time":196849,"text":"We will be able to see the velocity of the car in front of us,"},{"time":199220,"text":"to see how fast that guy's going or stopping."},{"time":202460,"text":"If that guy's going down to zero, I'll know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206970,"text":"And with computation and algorithms and predictive models,"},{"time":210829,"text":"we will be able to see the future."},{"time":214102,"text":"You may think that's impossible."},{"time":215658,"text":"How can you predict the future? That's really hard."},{"time":218389,"text":"Actually, no. With cars, it's not impossible."},{"time":222008,"text":"Cars are three-dimensional objects"},{"time":224740,"text":"that have a fixed position and velocity."},{"time":227072,"text":"They travel down roads."},{"time":228703,"text":"Often they travel on pre-published routes."},{"time":231115,"text":"It's really not that hard to make reasonable predictions"},{"time":235053,"text":"about where a car's going to be in the near future."},{"time":237917,"text":"Even if, when you're in your car"},{"time":239919,"text":"and some motorcyclist comes -- bshoom! --"},{"time":241913,"text":"85 miles an hour down, lane-splitting --"},{"time":244209,"text":"I know you've had this experience --"},{"time":246756,"text":"that guy didn't \"just come out of nowhere.\""},{"time":249359,"text":"That guy's been on the road probably for the last half hour."},{"time":253002,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":254192,"text":"Right? I mean, somebody's seen him."},{"time":257781,"text":"Ten, 20, 30 miles back, someone's seen that guy,"},{"time":260549,"text":"and as soon as one car sees that guy"},{"time":262933,"text":"and puts him on the map, he's on the map --"},{"time":265164,"text":"position, velocity,"},{"time":267340,"text":"good estimate he'll continue going 85 miles an hour."},{"time":269661,"text":"You'll know, because your car will know, because"},{"time":271845,"text":"that other car will have whispered something in his ear,"},{"time":274120,"text":"like, \"By the way, five minutes,"},{"time":276043,"text":"motorcyclist, watch out.\""},{"time":278818,"text":"You can make reasonable predictions about how cars behave."},{"time":281521,"text":"I mean, they're Newtonian objects."},{"time":282886,"text":"That's very nice about them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285795,"text":"So how do we get there?"},{"time":288829,"text":"We can start with something as simple"},{"time":291095,"text":"as sharing our position data between cars,"},{"time":293965,"text":"just sharing GPS."},{"time":295857,"text":"If I have a GPS and a camera in my car,"},{"time":298301,"text":"I have a pretty precise idea of where I am"},{"time":300532,"text":"and how fast I'm going."},{"time":302264,"text":"With computer vision, I can estimate where"},{"time":303921,"text":"the cars around me are, sort of, and where they're going."},{"time":307458,"text":"And same with the other cars."},{"time":308428,"text":"They can have a precise idea of where they are,"},{"time":310242,"text":"and sort of a vague idea of where the other cars are."},{"time":312388,"text":"What happens if two cars share that data,"},{"time":315619,"text":"if they talk to each other?"},{"time":317574,"text":"I can tell you exactly what happens."},{"time":320352,"text":"Both models improve."},{"time":322691,"text":"Everybody wins."},{"time":324746,"text":"Professor Bob Wang and his team"},{"time":327323,"text":"have done computer simulations of what happens"},{"time":330061,"text":"when fuzzy estimates combine, even in light traffic,"},{"time":333492,"text":"when cars just share GPS data,"},{"time":336116,"text":"and we've moved this research out of the computer simulation"},{"time":338629,"text":"and into robot test beds that have the actual sensors"},{"time":341656,"text":"that are in cars now on these robots:"},{"time":344789,"text":"stereo cameras, GPS,"},{"time":346627,"text":"and the two-dimensional laser range finders"},{"time":348501,"text":"that are common in backup systems."},{"time":350741,"text":"We also attach a discrete short-range communication radio,"},{"time":355225,"text":"and the robots talk to each other."},{"time":357134,"text":"When these robots come at each other,"},{"time":358673,"text":"they track each other's position precisely,"},{"time":361644,"text":"and they can avoid each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364381,"text":"We're now adding more and more robots into the mix,"},{"time":367607,"text":"and we encountered some problems."},{"time":369078,"text":"One of the problems, when you get too much chatter,"},{"time":371437,"text":"it's hard to process all the packets, so you have to prioritize,"},{"time":375165,"text":"and that's where the predictive model helps you."},{"time":377522,"text":"If your robot cars are all tracking the predicted trajectories,"},{"time":381894,"text":"you don't pay as much attention to those packets."},{"time":383661,"text":"You prioritize the one guy"},{"time":385364,"text":"who seems to be going a little off course."},{"time":386697,"text":"That guy could be a problem."},{"time":389223,"text":"And you can predict the new trajectory."},{"time":392225,"text":"So you don't only know that he's going off course, you know how."},{"time":394988,"text":"And you know which drivers you need to alert to get out of the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398713,"text":"And we wanted to do -- how can we best alert everyone?"},{"time":401346,"text":"How can these cars whisper, \"You need to get out of the way?\""},{"time":404529,"text":"Well, it depends on two things:"},{"time":406046,"text":"one, the ability of the car,"},{"time":408215,"text":"and second the ability of the driver."},{"time":411432,"text":"If one guy has a really great car,"},{"time":412937,"text":"but they're on their phone or, you know, doing something,"},{"time":415862,"text":"they're not probably in the best position"},{"time":417792,"text":"to react in an emergency."},{"time":420762,"text":"So we started a separate line of research"},{"time":422427,"text":"doing driver state modeling."},{"time":424978,"text":"And now, using a series of three cameras,"},{"time":427307,"text":"we can detect if a driver is looking forward,"},{"time":429577,"text":"looking away, looking down, on the phone,"},{"time":432437,"text":"or having a cup of coffee."},{"time":435498,"text":"We can predict the accident"},{"time":437568,"text":"and we can predict who, which cars,"},{"time":441219,"text":"are in the best position to move out of the way"},{"time":444705,"text":"to calculate the safest route for everyone."},{"time":447714,"text":"Fundamentally, these technologies exist today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452349,"text":"I think the biggest problem that we face"},{"time":455173,"text":"is our own willingness to share our data."},{"time":458186,"text":"I think it's a very disconcerting notion,"},{"time":460817,"text":"this idea that our cars will be watching us,"},{"time":463203,"text":"talking about us to other cars,"},{"time":466574,"text":"that we'll be going down the road in a sea of gossip."},{"time":470001,"text":"But I believe it can be done in a way that protects our privacy,"},{"time":473898,"text":"just like right now, when I look at your car from the outside,"},{"time":477639,"text":"I don't really know about you."},{"time":480002,"text":"If I look at your license plate number,"},{"time":481139,"text":"I don't really know who you are."},{"time":483025,"text":"I believe our cars can talk about us behind our backs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487274,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":490249,"text":"And I think it's going to be a great thing."},{"time":493434,"text":"I want you to consider for a moment"},{"time":495084,"text":"if you really don't want the distracted teenager behind you"},{"time":499202,"text":"to know that you're braking,"},{"time":501322,"text":"that you're coming to a dead stop."},{"time":504246,"text":"By sharing our data willingly,"},{"time":506987,"text":"we can do what's best for everyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509799,"text":"So let your car gossip about you."},{"time":512875,"text":"It's going to make the roads a lot safer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515913,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517704,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}